h2. Aaron Patterson

Mild mannered Ruby programmer by day, internetexpert by night. When Aaron Patterson is not perusing pictures of cute kittens, he is making rails scale to at least 82pt font for his employer, AT&amp;T interactive.

His open source contributions include, but are not limited to:

* Nokogiri
* Mechanize
* Enterprise! the gem.

You can find him in Seattle, Tuesday nights, hacking with the other members of Seattle.rb.

h3. Upcoming Events

